Sentencas: A dendritic porous supported microstructure simultaneously creates small pore size and broad gas diffusion pathways in a solid oxide fuel cell anode membrane.
Titulo: High performance anode with dendritic porous structure for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This micro-structure also achieves pore sizes that reduce with increasing depth within the membrane without increasing the structure tortuosity.
Titulo: High performance anode with dendritic porous structure for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Such a microstructure supplies high triple phase boundary density, fast gas diffusion and low polarization resistance.
Titulo: High performance anode with dendritic porous structure for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Here we characterise the performance of a porous anode with such a dendritic microstructure.
Titulo: High performance anode with dendritic porous structure for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The solid oxide fuel cell with this high performance anode achieved 0.92 W cm(-2 )power density at 600 degrees C. Crown Copyright (C) 2018
Titulo: High performance anode with dendritic porous structure for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells
